     <body>
     <div type="poem">
   <pb facs="9"/>
   <head>¶The Glory of the Honorable, is
the feare of God.</head>
   <p>
      <figure>
         <l>The Beare doth beare me now in hand</l>
         <l>that Noble is thy race.</l>
         <l>The vertues of thy worthy minde,</l>
         <l>shevve forth the gifts of grace.</l>
      </figure>
   </p>
</div>
